text: Anna Harr is an American actress. She is known for her work on the films Stasis, Bethany and Krampus Origins. ==Life and career== Anna was born in Phoenix, Arizona. In 2017, she was cast in a role as Bethany/Young Claire in the film Bethany and played a lead role in the film Stasis, later released by Netflix.
